<section id="about" class="py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-7xl">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-display font-bold text-dark-900 mb-8 leading-tight">
          Acerca de <span class="text-primary-yellow">DasPix</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Somos un equipo de desarrolladores apasionados por crear soluciones digitales que transforman la forma en que las empresas interactúan con sus clientes.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Fundada con un enfoque en la excelencia y un equipo lleno de talento joven, DasPix es el mejor aliado para llevar tu presencia digital al siguiente nivel con innovación y calidad.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-12">
          <div class="text-center p-6 bg-primary-cream/50 rounded-xl border border-primary-cream hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary-blue mb-3">10+</div>
            <div class="text-md font-medium text-gray-600">Proyectos Completados</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-6 bg-primary-cream/50 rounded-xl border border-primary-cream hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary-coral mb-3">2+</div>
            <div class="text-md font-medium text-gray-600">Años de Experiencia</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-6 bg-primary-cream/50 rounded-xl border border-primary-cream hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary-yellow mb-3">40+</div>
            <div class="text-md font-medium text-gray-600">Clientes Satisfechos</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-6 bg-primary-cream/50 rounded-xl border border-primary-cream hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary-blue mb-3">24/7</div>
            <div class="text-md font-medium text-gray-600">Soporte</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <span class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-primary-blue/10 text-primary-blue rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-primary-blue/20 hover:bg-primary-blue hover:text-white transition">React</span>
          <span class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-primary-coral/10 text-primary-coral rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-primary-coral/20 hover:bg-primary-coral hover:text-white transition">Node.js</span>
          <span class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-primary-yellow/10 text-dark-900 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-primary-yellow/20 hover:bg-primary-yellow hover:text-dark-900 transition">WordPress</span>
          <span class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-primary-cream/20 text-dark-900 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-primary-cream/30 hover:bg-primary-cream transition">Shopify</span>
          <span class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-gray-200 text-dark-900 rounded-full text-sm font-medium hover:bg-gray-300 transition">AWS</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 relative">
        <div class="relative group">
          <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3184291/pexels-photo-3184291.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" alt="Equipo DasPix trabajando" class="rounded-3xl shadow-2xl transform group-hover:scale-[1.01] transition duration-500">
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-36 h-36 bg-primary-yellow rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-xl border-4 border-white">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-dark-900">100%</div>
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-dark-700">Satisfacción</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Floating elements -->
        <div class="absolute -top-6 -left-6 w-24 h-24 bg-primary-blue/20 rounded-full animate-float z-0"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-1/2 -right-8 w-20 h-20 bg-primary-coral/20 rounded-full animate-float z-0" style="animation-delay: -2s;"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Team Values -->
    <div class="mt-28 px-4">
      <h3 class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-center text-dark-900 mb-16">Nuestros Valores</h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-blue to-primary-blue/80 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark-900 mb-4 text-center">Calidad Primero</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-center leading-relaxed">Compromiso inquebrantable con la excelencia, entregando siempre productos de máxima calidad que superan expectativas.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-coral to-primary-coral/80 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark-900 mb-4 text-center">Enfocados en ti</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-center leading-relaxed">Tu éxito es nuestro éxito. Trabajamos codo a codo contigo para entender y satisfacer todas tus necesidades digitales.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-yellow to-primary-yellow/80 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark-900 mb-4 text-center">Innovación</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-center leading-relaxed">Nos mantenemos a la vanguardia, adoptando las últimas tecnologías para ofrecerte soluciones modernas y disruptivas.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>